          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/867_.step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once browned, add the <strong>chipotle paste</strong> and<strong> tomato paste</strong> and cook for 30 sec</p>\r\n<p>Add 150ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[300ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> and cook, covered, for 10-15 min or until the <strong>chicken</strong> is cooked throug<span class=\"text-highlight\">h (no pink meat!)</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
